      "id": "PopularPost177127",
      "post_content": "This card is totally unplayable. Here is a discard spell that costs **MORE** than [Mind Rot](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mind Rot) and [Stupor](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Stupor) to hit a player with two random discards. [Hymn to Tourach](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Hymn to Tourach) aside, this card should read:\n  \n   \nFlay, 1BB sorcery\n  \nTarget player discards two cards from his or her hand. That player may pay 1. If he or she does not that player discards two cards at random instead.\n  \n   ",
