      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost177127\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_post\">This card is totally unplayable. Here is a discard spell that costs <b>MORE</b> than <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Mind Rot\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mind Rot\">Mind Rot</a> and <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Stupor\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Stupor\">Stupor</a> to hit a player with two random discards. <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Hymn to Tourach\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Hymn to Tourach\">Hymn to Tourach</a> aside, this card should read:\r<br/> <br/>Flay, 1BB sorcery\r<br/>Target player discards two cards from his or her hand. That player may pay 1. If he or she does not that player discards two cards at random instead.\r<br/> <br/></span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '177127'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy65832\">lich000</span>\r\n                                (7/9/2011 6:55:36 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubC