      "id": "PopularPost278347",
      "post_content": "I realize it's not fair to compare this to [Hymn to Tourach](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Hymn to Tourach), though it has that effect. However, did they really need to make it cost the same CMC as two [Specter's Wail](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Specter's Wail)s (a fairly bad card!) AND give the opponent a way to lessen the pain? ![2](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=2&type=symbol)![Black](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=B&type=symbol) would have been a more reasonable cost for what this card does. It would rival [Stupor](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Stupor) and [Mind Rot](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mind Rot).",
      "posted_by": "LordZogar",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost278347\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_post\">I realize it's not fair to compare this to <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Hymn to Tourach\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Hymn to Tourach\">Hymn to Tourach</a>, though it has that effect.  However, did they really need to make it cost the same CMC as two <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Specter's Wail\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Specter's Wail\">Specter's Wail</a>s (a fairly bad card!) AND give the opponent a way to lessen the pain?  <img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"2\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=2&amp;type=symbol\"/><img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"Black\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=B&amp;type=symbol\"/> would have been a more reasonable cost for what this card does.  It would rival <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Stupor\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Stupor\">Stupor</a> and <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Mind Rot\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mind Rot\">Mind Rot</a>.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '278347'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy308\">LordZogar</span>\r\n                                (10/26/2012 7:18:08 A